1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:41,070
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty Ⅱ : To The West]

3
00:01:41,390 --> 00:01:43,990
[Episode 1]

4
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:50,390
[Chengfo Temple, Chang'an]

5
00:01:47,750 --> 00:01:50,210
During the Yanhe period of the Tang Dynasty,

6
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,710
the greatest painter of Tang,

7
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:53,759
Qin Xiaobai,

8
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:55,320
was invited by the princess

9
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:57,870
to stay in Chengfo Temple in Chang'an

10
00:01:58,390 --> 00:02:00,710
and paint the illustration of Mara's Defeat

11
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:03,950
to pray for the late Heavenly Empress.

12
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:18,450
[Great Buddha Hall]

13
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:29,540
[Qin Xiaobai, a painter from Chang'an]

14
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:52,340
He's about to draw the eyes.

15
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:53,500
It'll make my day.

16
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:55,070
I'm grateful to have been born in Chang'an

17
00:03:55,070 --> 00:03:56,670
so I can witness this moment.

18
00:03:56,829 --> 00:03:57,630
Yes.

19
00:03:58,390 --> 00:03:59,350
Be quiet.

20
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:02,870
Why is he leaving?

21
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,310
Yeah, why is he leaving?

22
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:06,230
Why?

23
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,230
Why is he leaving?

24
00:04:21,589 --> 00:04:22,550
In terms of murals,

25
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:24,030
the illustration of hell is hard enough.

26
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:26,270
The illustration of Mara's Defeat is even harder.

27
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:28,150
It's said Her Highness has long put it on the agenda.

28
00:04:28,150 --> 00:04:30,050
But no one but Master Qin

29
00:04:30,110 --> 00:04:32,710
can complete this task.

30
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,390
It's such a difficult mural,

31
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,310
but you've nearly finished it

32
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,970
just a few days after arrival.

33
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,550
You're so talented.

34
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:40,120
Yes.

35
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:40,750
Mara.

36
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:41,590
Mara's three daughters.

37
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:42,390
The Mara Army.

38
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,909
They're all lifelike.

39
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:46,230
But the finishing touch…

40
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,190
Yes.

41
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,670
I heard that you've been hesitating for three days

42
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:50,690
and still haven't done it.

43
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:53,020
Are you waiting for an auspicious moment?

44
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:54,270
Can you tell us

45
00:04:54,310 --> 00:04:55,670
when you'll finish the mural?

46
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:57,190
I'll wait in the temple in advance

47
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:58,909
to feast my eyes.

48
00:04:58,909 --> 00:04:59,240
Yeah.

49
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,110
That's right.

50
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,550
Giving Mara eyes

51
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,750
will make him come to life.

52
00:05:04,590 --> 00:05:07,030
Aren't you afraid of him coming off the wall

53
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,160
and killing you?

54
00:05:15,710 --> 00:05:16,470
Ridiculous!

55
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:22,990
Chief Musician.

56
00:05:22,990 --> 00:05:23,800
You've also seen

57
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,260
the mural in Chengfo Temple.

58
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,390
Master Qin is here.

59
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:27,930
Won't you make a toast to him?

60
00:05:27,930 --> 00:05:28,980
Master?

61
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:30,350
Where?

62
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,040
Why can't I see any masters?

63
00:05:34,990 --> 00:05:36,320
Master Qin. Master Qin.

64
00:05:36,590 --> 00:05:37,350
Calm down.

65
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,630
The Chief Musician

66
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,640
is definitely drunk.

67
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,670
Come to life?

68
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,909
How arrogant!

69
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:44,560
[Sun Wang, the Chief Musician]

70
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,310
Is Chang'an so big

71
00:05:43,620 --> 00:05:44,710
that you've forgotten

72
00:05:44,710 --> 00:05:46,110
your place, Mr. Painter?

73
00:05:46,909 --> 00:05:47,240
You…

74
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:50,350
Bastard!

75
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:52,600
Once Mara comes to life,

76
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,470
he'll kill you first.

77
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:09,000
The best painter in Tang

78
00:06:09,930 --> 00:06:12,570
doesn't get to live the life I do.

79
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:35,740
[Mara's Defeat]

80
00:06:47,230 --> 00:06:48,360
Victim identified.

81
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,310
He's Sun Wang, the Chief Musician.

82
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,640
His liver was taken too.

83
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:01,960
He died about four o'clock a.m.

84
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,510
There's a slash on his front,

85
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,800
stretching from his shoulder to his ribs.

86
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,400
Very deep.

87
00:07:06,020 --> 00:07:07,020
His liver is gone.

88
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:08,430
His eyes are wide open

89
00:07:08,690 --> 00:07:10,110
as if he'd seen something horrifying

90
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:11,030
before he died.

91
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,550
What makes him different

92
00:07:12,550 --> 00:07:13,630
from the previous two victims

93
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:15,040
is the slash.

94
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,350
It's long and deep.

95
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:24,950
He was hurt by a big sword.

96
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:25,930
More specific.

97
00:07:26,710 --> 00:07:27,770
What kind of sword?

98
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,910
A sword that's very long

99
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:30,990
and very big.

100
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,560
There are four types of swords in Tang.

101
00:07:32,470 --> 00:07:35,520
[Lu Lingfeng, Deputy President of the Supreme Court]

102
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:34,630
Yi swords.

103
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:35,580
Zhang swords.

104
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:36,230
Heng swords.

105
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:36,830
Mo swords.

106
00:07:38,590 --> 00:07:40,270
The slash goes across his torso

107
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:41,550
and is very deep.

108
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:44,110
It must be the Mo sword.

109
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:45,750
Yes.

110
00:07:46,150 --> 00:07:47,790
Mr. Lu, you hit the nail on the head.

111
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:48,830
I feel ashamed.

112
00:07:49,150 --> 00:07:50,470
The Mo sword is lethal.

113
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,420
Its use is strictly regulated.

114
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:53,240
In the central Shaanxi plain and the Central Plain,

115
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:55,280
[Guo Zhuang]

116
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,330
the troops guarding the two capitals

117
00:07:55,990 --> 00:07:57,230
are not equipped with this kind of sword.

118
00:07:57,230 --> 00:07:57,750
Right.

119
00:07:58,909 --> 00:08:00,440
The Mo sword is usually used

120
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,340
by armies defending the borders,

121
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,010
like the Anxi Army.

122
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:07,000
Why did it suddenly appear in the capital?

123
00:08:12,270 --> 00:08:13,330
What's that scent?

124
00:08:14,910 --> 00:08:16,430
There was balm behind the victim's ear.

125
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:17,960
The scent should be from it.

126
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:19,560
Every detail is recorded.

127
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:20,690
The balm I collected

128
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:21,660
is here.

129
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:24,470
I think

130
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,710
it's a kind of lip balm for women.

131
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:29,060
But I don't know lady stuff.

132
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:31,150
So I can't tell what kind of

133
00:08:31,430 --> 00:08:32,470
lip balm it is.

134
00:08:37,730 --> 00:08:39,970
[Pei Xijun]

135
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,610
This is Black Balm.

136
00:08:43,549 --> 00:08:44,210
Black Balm?

137
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:46,270
It's a kind of dark red lip balm

138
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:49,630
[Innocent and Elegant]

139
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:47,550
from Dunhuang.

140
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,750
In recent months,

141
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,180
it's become popular in the capital.

142
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:52,310
But it was raining until this morning.

143
00:08:52,350 --> 00:08:53,550
How could the lip balm

144
00:08:53,570 --> 00:08:55,120
still have such a strong scent?

145
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,160
Scented lip balms

146
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:57,910
are common.

147
00:08:58,550 --> 00:09:00,790
But it's indeed strange that the scent still lingered

148
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,920
after a rainy night.

149
00:09:02,790 --> 00:09:04,450
If only Chicken Fed were here.

150
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,910
He definitely knows what this scent is.

151
00:09:10,450 --> 00:09:11,310
Why are you asking

152
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:12,270
about makeup?

153
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:14,190
Are you buying me a gift?

154
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,360
Black Balm is very expensive.

155
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:20,070
Mr. Lu,

156
00:09:20,170 --> 00:09:21,230
we found a witness.

157
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:22,780
An old man living nearby

158
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:24,110
got up to close the window that night

159
00:09:24,110 --> 00:09:25,550
and saw Sun Wang being killed.

160
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:27,030
Did he see the murderer?

161
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:27,990
Yes.

162
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:28,910
But…

163
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:31,680
it was not human.

164
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,470
What?

165
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:37,020
I thought you left.

166
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:38,990
I don't like makeup.

167
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:40,430
I won't blame you

168
00:09:40,450 --> 00:09:42,110
even if you never buy it for me.

169
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:43,590
It's not about Black Balm.

170
00:09:43,590 --> 00:09:44,470
I want you

171
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:45,930
to draw a painting according to

172
00:09:45,930 --> 00:09:47,530
the witness's description.

173
00:09:47,550 --> 00:09:48,310
When?

174
00:09:48,830 --> 00:09:49,310
Now.

175
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:50,840
The sooner, the better.

176
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:52,990
No.

177
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:54,990
I'm going to Chengfo Temple.

178
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,230
Qin Xiaobai is going to

179
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:57,510
finish Mara's Defeat today.

180
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,040
This is a rare opportunity.

181
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:01,440
In the past 10 days,

182
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:03,060
three men have been killed in the capital.

183
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:04,310
They died horrifying deaths,

184
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:05,590
and their livers were taken.

185
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:06,990
They were all officials.

186
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,530
I'm asking you to paint

187
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,690
to catch the murderer

188
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,090
so peace can be restored.

189
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:12,720
Lu Lingfeng.

190
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,610
Don't be angry.

191
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:14,550
I didn't know

192
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:15,680
it was so important.

193
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:16,970
I'll go with you, okay?

194
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:20,990
Very big.

195
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:22,110
Very high.

196
00:10:23,070 --> 00:10:23,670
Very high?

197
00:10:23,690 --> 00:10:24,060
Yes.

198
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:26,020
On the back of a monster.

199
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:27,310
Very scary.

200
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,400
[Cloud Tower]

201
00:10:28,610 --> 00:10:30,410
I was put on the spot at that time.

202
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:31,720
Everyone knows

203
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:33,980
Her Highness paid a hefty sum to bring Qin Xiaobai

204
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:35,300
to the capital.

205
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:36,810
The Chief Musician

206
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:38,880
was also promoted by Her Highness.

207
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:40,470
It just

208
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:41,810
didn't make sense.

209
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:43,950
Was he a regular?

210
00:10:44,270 --> 00:10:44,750
Yes.

211
00:10:45,070 --> 00:10:46,470
He came almost every day.

212
00:10:46,990 --> 00:10:48,120
The Chief Musician,

213
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:49,630
an eighth-ranked official,

214
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,690
came to Cloud Tower, the most expensive

215
00:10:50,690 --> 00:10:52,150
restaurant in Chang'an, every day.

216
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:53,150
He was quite rich.

217
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,750
You misunderstood.

218
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:57,680
[Bi Chengye, the owner of Cloud Tower]

219
00:10:55,230 --> 00:10:56,860
Every piece of music played here

220
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:58,380
was revised by him.

221
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,510
When he drank here,

222
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:00,950
I wouldn't ask him to pay.

223
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:05,470
When was that?

224
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:09,210
A little past 9 p.m.

225
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:11,560
Sun Wang used to be a vet.

226
00:11:11,950 --> 00:11:13,140
Last month, by River Qu,

227
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:14,430
he treated Her Highness' horse

228
00:11:14,430 --> 00:11:15,270
and played konghou

229
00:11:15,270 --> 00:11:16,230
by chance.

230
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:17,750
Her Highness heard it

231
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:18,650
and ordered him

232
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:20,470
to play dozens of other instruments.

233
00:11:20,470 --> 00:11:21,870
He was good at all of them.

234
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,550
Her Highness was pleased

235
00:11:23,590 --> 00:11:24,930
and transferred him from the Court of the Imperial Stud

236
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:26,440
to the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

237
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,630
A vet

238
00:11:28,430 --> 00:11:30,090
who was also a great musician?

239
00:11:31,070 --> 00:11:32,140
How interesting.

240
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,690
Where are you going?

241
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,750
Since there is no clue in the Court of Imperial Sacrifices,

242
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:38,490
I'll go to the Court of the Imperial Stud.

243
00:11:38,490 --> 00:11:42,230
[Loyalty and Devotion]

244
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:40,030
In the last year,

245
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:41,310
the place Sun Wang

246
00:11:41,530 --> 00:11:43,230
went to the most often to treat horses

247
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:46,240
was the residence of General Ma Xiong of the Anxi Army.

248
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:52,080
[Ma's Mansion]

249
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:58,980
Sirs,

250
00:11:58,090 --> 00:12:00,820
[Mrs. Ma]

251
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:02,110
what can I do for you?

252
00:12:02,990 --> 00:12:04,650
Is it General Ma's residence?

253
00:12:05,430 --> 00:12:08,630
We're government officials, here for a routine inquiry.

254
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:10,120
Dr. Sun

255
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:11,900
did treat my horses.

256
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:13,070
What's wrong?

257
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:13,910
He...

258
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,610
Nothing.

259
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:18,120
Just a routine inquiry.

260
00:12:18,350 --> 00:12:19,950
Is Dr. Sun a good vet?

261
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:23,030
Of course.

262
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:25,830
He's one of the best vets

263
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:27,730
in the Court of the Imperial Stud.

264
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:28,750
I doubt that.

265
00:12:29,230 --> 00:12:30,630
If he's really a good vet,

266
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,970
why did he come here

267
00:12:31,970 --> 00:12:33,430
dozens of times last year?

268
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:37,040
My husband works in the Anxi Army.

269
00:12:37,310 --> 00:12:38,630
Every time he came back,

270
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:40,490
he brought back some good horses.

271
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,100
So we keep many horses

272
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:44,070
in our stable.

273
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:50,790
My husband is a mobile corps commander,

274
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:51,980
a fifth-ranked official.

275
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:53,230
When his horses are sick,

276
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:54,390
ordinary vets

277
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:56,350
are not qualified to treat them.

278
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:58,430
So I had to send for Dr. Sun.

279
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:01,110
Dr. Sun is a great vet,

280
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,790
but some horses

281
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:05,660
needed to be treated several times

282
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,830
to fully recover.

283
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:10,190
I see.

284
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:11,870
I love horses too.

285
00:13:12,070 --> 00:13:13,270
Can I see your horses?

286
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:14,990
Sure.

287
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:16,830
You keep so many horses

288
00:13:16,830 --> 00:13:18,090
at your own residence.

289
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,550
It's enviable.

290
00:13:21,150 --> 00:13:23,310
My husband got these horses

291
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:25,390
when he was away fighting in battles.

292
