585
00:26:39,250 --> 00:26:40,590
by that lady.

586
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,150
Get her here to learn from me.

587
00:26:42,150 --> 00:26:44,020
I'll teach her everything for free.

588
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:45,450
She'll definitely become

589
00:26:45,450 --> 00:26:47,450
the next most famous person in Tang.

590
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:48,630
Crazy.

591
00:26:55,940 --> 00:26:56,920
I found a few stores

592
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,120
that sell Black Balm.

593
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:00,040
But the Black Balm they sell

594
00:27:00,390 --> 00:27:01,790
doesn't have this scent.

595
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:03,930
Do you not want to eat anymore?

596
00:27:04,070 --> 00:27:05,130
I don't have to eat.

597
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,010
Just buy me a drink.

598
00:27:07,190 --> 00:27:08,830
You should be too ashamed to drink!

599
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:10,630
According to a reliable source,

600
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:12,270
at the Ghost Market,

601
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,640
someone once bought Black Balm

602
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,790
with a long-lasting fragrance.

603
00:27:18,230 --> 00:27:19,510
But it's hard to buy it.

604
00:27:19,990 --> 00:27:20,710
At the Ghost Market,

605
00:27:20,710 --> 00:27:22,470
there's a place called Carefree.

606
00:27:22,470 --> 00:27:23,290
You must drink up

607
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:24,380
a whole jar of wine

608
00:27:24,670 --> 00:27:27,070
before the female owner takes the balm out.

609
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:29,170
You can't fool me, Guo Zhuang.

610
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:31,310
You just need an excuse

611
00:27:31,330 --> 00:27:32,390
to drink your fill.

612
00:27:36,670 --> 00:27:37,450
The Ghost Market is dangerous.

613
00:27:37,450 --> 00:27:39,030
How many guards should we bring?

614
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:40,150
You and I are enough.

615
00:27:40,150 --> 00:27:42,480
Will you pay for the other guards' drinks?

616
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:49,140
[Ghost Market]

617
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:53,480
Look at this.

618
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,360
Carefree?

619
00:28:00,190 --> 00:28:01,350
I came to the Ghost Market several times

620
00:28:01,350 --> 00:28:02,480
for investigation.

621
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:04,870
I don't remember this store.

622
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:06,380
It's new.

623
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:08,440
[Carefree]

624
00:28:06,910 --> 00:28:08,190
The Ghost Market has been bustling lately.

625
00:28:08,190 --> 00:28:09,570
Here, you can buy all the fine wines

626
00:28:09,570 --> 00:28:10,480
you can't find outside.

627
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,590
Even the dancers in Resentment Tower

628
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:12,990
are younger than before.

629
00:28:14,670 --> 00:28:15,710
You've been there?

630
00:28:15,710 --> 00:28:16,390
No.

631
00:28:17,190 --> 00:28:18,270
Just hearsay.

632
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:26,190
Sirs,

633
00:28:26,990 --> 00:28:29,190
what would you like to order?

634
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,030
Get your boss here.

635
00:28:32,590 --> 00:28:33,990
I'm the boss.

636
00:28:35,830 --> 00:28:36,690
Don't lie to me.

637
00:28:37,630 --> 00:28:39,470
We're here to see if the rumor is true.

638
00:28:39,470 --> 00:28:40,350
People say

639
00:28:40,470 --> 00:28:41,630
the owner of this shop

640
00:28:41,630 --> 00:28:42,910
is a gorgeous lady.

641
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,430
She can't be you.

642
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:48,710
So,

643
00:28:49,340 --> 00:28:53,230
whenever you hear about a beautiful woman,

644
00:28:53,870 --> 00:28:56,870
you'll go meet her in person?

645
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:57,950
Yes.

646
00:29:04,470 --> 00:29:05,430
I'm quite good-looking

647
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:06,750
after all.

648
00:29:17,950 --> 00:29:20,990
[The owner of Carefree]

649
00:29:23,630 --> 00:29:24,310
Illusion?

650
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:26,190
You came out of nowhere.

651
00:29:26,190 --> 00:29:27,590
That was not an illusion.

652
00:29:28,350 --> 00:29:30,750
Last night, some customers left very late.

653
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:31,810
I didn't sleep well

654
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,860
and didn't feel like dressing up.

655
00:29:34,870 --> 00:29:37,000
Then I was despised by this gentleman.

656
00:29:37,350 --> 00:29:38,480
That's more like it.

657
00:29:38,740 --> 00:29:40,540
Bring me good food and fine wine.

658
00:29:40,630 --> 00:29:41,830
You'll drink with me.

659
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,680
That's not how it works.

660
00:29:47,100 --> 00:29:48,670
They won't allow it.

661
00:29:51,390 --> 00:29:52,650
It's Carefree's rule.

662
00:29:52,820 --> 00:29:54,330
You have to finish a jar of wine

663
00:29:54,330 --> 00:29:55,730
before drinking with me.

664
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:57,540
If you can drink more,

665
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,390
I have two sisters.

666
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:02,110
Bring them wine.

667
00:30:08,340 --> 00:30:09,240
Drink up.

668
00:30:09,770 --> 00:30:11,710
If other customers finish their wine first,

669
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:13,040
you won't have a chance.

670
00:30:37,230 --> 00:30:38,290
This wine is light.

671
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:40,210
It's easy to finish a jar of it.

672
00:30:42,460 --> 00:30:43,030
Brother,

673
00:30:43,930 --> 00:30:44,950
here's to you.

674
00:30:55,670 --> 00:30:57,270
My friend is a lightweight.

675
00:30:57,820 --> 00:30:59,680
I shouldn't have brought him out.

676
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,310
Miss,

677
00:31:41,180 --> 00:31:42,240
you kept your word.

678
00:31:42,390 --> 00:31:43,470
Actually, I'm here today

679
00:31:43,470 --> 00:31:44,470
to buy Black Balm,

680
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:46,290
the kind with a long-lasting fragrance.

681
00:31:46,290 --> 00:31:47,300
I guessed it.

682
00:31:47,710 --> 00:31:48,770
Black Balm, right?

683
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:50,760
It's on the lips of my two sisters.

684
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:52,240
Take

685
00:31:52,610 --> 00:31:53,740
as much as you want.

686
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,110
Go!

687
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,590
Who are you?

688
00:33:53,150 --> 00:33:55,130
I'm Lu Lingfeng, Deputy President of the Supreme Court.

689
00:33:55,130 --> 00:33:57,190
Remove your disguise and surrender.

690
00:33:57,570 --> 00:33:58,900
If you were really Mara,

691
00:33:58,950 --> 00:34:00,190
you'd have eaten me alive.

692
00:34:00,190 --> 00:34:00,850
Otherwise,

693
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:03,130
why are you using the Mo sword of Tang?

694
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,520
Mr. Lu, move aside!

695
00:34:41,889 --> 00:34:43,480
Go!

696
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:46,030
Guo Zhuang!

697
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:29,120
[Su Wuming, Assistant of Qianling Mausoleum]

698
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:33,670
[Yingtao]

699
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:35,260
Wow.

700
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:37,420
You didn't know how to fish a few days ago,

701
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,870
but you're a master now.

702
00:35:40,230 --> 00:35:42,470
That's an exaggeration.

703
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:44,710
A master of fishing

704
00:35:44,770 --> 00:35:46,770
is a master of timing.

705
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,740
I'm fishing

706
00:35:49,350 --> 00:35:50,620
for fish stew.

707
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,670
Braised fish is the best.

708
00:35:54,430 --> 00:35:54,960
Yingtao.

709
00:35:55,430 --> 00:35:57,910
Why don't you learn to make braised fish?

710
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:01,230
You're pushing your luck.

711
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:03,650
Have you really taken me as your maid?

712
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:04,800
Another one.

713
00:36:06,580 --> 00:36:07,630
What a big fish!

714
00:36:09,470 --> 00:36:10,420
Here.

715
00:36:10,790 --> 00:36:11,510
Tonight,

716
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:13,880
practice making braised fish with it.

717
00:36:13,910 --> 00:36:14,470
Okay.

718
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:26,640
[The government office of Qianling]

719
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:25,630
I'm Su Wuming, Assistant of Qianling Mausoleum.

720
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:26,790
Greetings, Mr. Bai.

721
00:36:27,870 --> 00:36:29,270
What brings you…

722
00:36:29,290 --> 00:36:30,950
The crown prince wants you back immediately.

723
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:31,880
Come with me now.

724
00:36:35,150 --> 00:36:35,910
Mr. Bai.

725
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:38,730
The quiet Qianling Mausoleum is perfect

726
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:40,230
for cultivating one's character.

727
00:36:40,230 --> 00:36:40,870
Su Wuming…

728
00:36:42,390 --> 00:36:43,150
No.

729
00:36:43,750 --> 00:36:45,030
It's my honor and duty

730
00:36:45,050 --> 00:36:46,030
to guard the mausoleum

731
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:48,030
for Emperor Gaozong and the Heavenly Empress.

732
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:49,030
In the past month,

733
00:36:49,130 --> 00:36:50,690
I've been getting along well

734
00:36:50,690 --> 00:36:52,090
with my colleagues here.

735
00:36:52,480 --> 00:36:53,610
I don't think I should go back

736
00:36:53,610 --> 00:36:54,470
to the capital.

737
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:57,250
Many strange things have happened in the capital recently.

738
00:36:54,750 --> 00:36:57,380
[Bai Shan, the crown prince's royal steward]

739
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:59,450
Lu Lingfeng, Deputy President of the Supreme Court,

740
00:36:59,450 --> 00:37:00,990
visited the Ghost Market at night

741
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:02,510
and encountered Mara.

742
00:37:02,870 --> 00:37:04,030
He's been missing for two days

743
00:37:04,030 --> 00:37:05,030
and may have died.

744
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:06,870
Lu Lingfeng…

745
00:37:06,910 --> 00:37:07,470
Now,

746
00:37:07,590 --> 00:37:09,320
the whole Chang'an is in panic.

747
00:37:09,790 --> 00:37:11,870
Someone took the chance to spread rumors,

748
00:37:11,870 --> 00:37:13,550
trying to destabilize the country.

749
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:14,150
This time,

750
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:16,310
His Majesty has ordered Detective Di's disciple,

751
00:37:16,310 --> 00:37:16,950
Su Wuming,

752
00:37:17,270 --> 00:37:18,670
to investigate the case.

753
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:21,910
Are you going to disobey His Majesty?

754
00:37:21,910 --> 00:37:22,550
No, no.

755
00:37:22,790 --> 00:37:23,890
Then get on the horse

756
00:37:23,890 --> 00:37:24,950
and go back with me.

757
00:37:29,270 --> 00:37:30,550
We need to hurry up.

758
00:37:30,950 --> 00:37:31,590
His Highness

759
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:33,520
will receive you at Jinguang Gate.

760
00:37:38,340 --> 00:37:40,530
[Long-lasting Peace]

761
00:37:39,590 --> 00:37:40,520
How is Qianling?

762
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:42,670
It's a blessed place

763
00:37:42,830 --> 00:37:44,470
with beautiful scenery.

764
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:45,910
Are there any ghosts?

765
00:37:46,590 --> 00:37:48,990
I don't believe in ghosts.

766
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:51,390
Why do you ask?

767
00:37:51,470 --> 00:37:52,390
If there are no ghosts at Qianling,

768
00:37:51,970 --> 00:37:54,800
[Crown Prince]

769
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:54,840
there can't be any in Chang'an.

770
00:37:56,630 --> 00:37:58,290
You're right, Your Highness.

771
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:01,110
I wonder what the Ministry of Personnel is thinking.

772
00:38:01,110 --> 00:38:03,040
His Majesty has summoned you back,

773
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:04,390
but they'll only make you

774
00:38:04,390 --> 00:38:06,390
the judicial adjutant of Yongzhou.

775
00:38:08,470 --> 00:38:09,330
Your Highness,

776
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:11,800
is it really His Majesty

777
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:14,120
who summoned me back?

778
00:38:15,390 --> 00:38:15,830
Yes.

779
00:38:17,050 --> 00:38:19,440
[Emperor]

780
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:19,020
The guy guarding Qianling,

781
00:38:19,020 --> 00:38:19,950
what's his name?

782
00:38:21,390 --> 00:38:22,230
Su Wuming.

783
00:38:23,750 --> 00:38:24,550
That's him.

784
00:38:25,540 --> 00:38:26,770
In Sky-scraping Tower,

785
00:38:26,770 --> 00:38:28,430
he had the guts to get in my way.

786
00:38:29,030 --> 00:38:29,870
Very bold.

787
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:33,280
He's also smart enough to take down Sass.

788
00:38:33,950 --> 00:38:35,080
Tell him to come back

789
00:38:35,470 --> 00:38:36,530
to crack this case.

790
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:37,750
Su Wuming.

791
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:39,540
Your teacher, Detective Di,

792
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:41,110
cracked many mysterious cases

793
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:43,370
and even saved the country from falling.

794
00:38:43,870 --> 00:38:44,550
Now,

795
00:38:45,590 --> 00:38:46,850
we're counting on you.

796
00:38:49,150 --> 00:38:50,270
Rest assured, Your Highness.

797
00:38:50,270 --> 00:38:52,990
I'll do my best.

798
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:05,750
Have you brought him back?

799
00:39:05,750 --> 00:39:07,460
[Prime Minister Cui, Secretariat Director]

800
00:39:06,350 --> 00:39:07,150
Yes.

801
00:39:09,660 --> 00:39:11,950
Greetings, Your Highness.

802
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:21,950
It took you four hours

803
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,530
to come back from Qianling.

804
00:39:23,790 --> 00:39:25,630
I should let you have a good rest,

805
00:39:25,790 --> 00:39:27,440
but the situation is urgent.

806
00:39:28,030 --> 00:39:28,830
Su Wuming.

807
00:39:29,430 --> 00:39:30,110
I order you

808
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:32,560
to find my Ji'er as soon as possible.

809
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:34,680
I don't understand what you mean.

810
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:36,710
Stop pretending.

811
00:39:36,790 --> 00:39:38,700
Lu Lingfeng is my Ji'er!

812
00:39:39,230 --> 00:39:41,920
He ran into Mara at the Ghost Market

813
00:39:41,950 --> 00:39:43,870
and is nowhere to be found now.

814
00:39:44,560 --> 00:39:46,620
I want you to find Ji'er immediately.

815
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:48,270
I want him alive.

816
00:39:48,470 --> 00:39:49,080
I want him

817
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,830
safe and sound!

818
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:57,350
On your way back,

819
00:39:58,310 --> 00:39:59,570
the crown prince's man

820
00:39:59,710 --> 00:40:01,700
must have told you

821
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:03,870
what happened in Chang'an.

822
00:40:03,950 --> 00:40:05,660
I've had a grasp of it.

823
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:07,880
What position have they promised you?

824
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:11,530
The Military Commander of Yongzhou.

825
00:40:13,270 --> 00:40:14,430
I knew it.

826
00:40:15,430 --> 00:40:16,910
To tell you the truth,

827
00:40:17,750 --> 00:40:19,630
it's my idea to make you

828
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:21,670
the judicial adjutant of Yongzhou.

829
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:23,390
I just want to see

830
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:26,070
how the Eastern Palace will bribe you.

831
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:29,170
Since you've been summoned back by His Majesty,

832
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:31,790
you should work for the Supreme Court.

833
00:40:32,720 --> 00:40:34,920
Lu Lingfeng has taken office.

834
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:37,530
But the Supreme Court needs two deputy presidents.

835
00:40:37,530 --> 00:40:38,700
It only has one now.

836
00:40:40,430 --> 00:40:41,760
You'll be the other one.

837
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:43,400
You'll take office tonight.

838
00:40:44,870 --> 00:40:45,730
Your Highness.

839
00:40:46,250 --> 00:40:48,000
Isn't it against the rules?

840
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:50,190
I know you.

841
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:55,200
I won't make you an informal official.

842
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:59,070
The appointment will arrive tomorrow at the latest.

843
00:40:59,790 --> 00:41:02,870
The seals of the Secretariat and the Chancellery,

844
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:05,070
together with His Majesty's stamp,

845
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:06,830
will all be on it.

846
00:41:10,170 --> 00:41:12,110
[Mortuary]

847
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:16,180
Kong Mao, a professor at the Imperial College,

848
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,110
died ten days ago

849
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,910
on his way home.

850
00:41:19,830 --> 00:41:22,550
There's no fatal wound on his body

851
00:41:23,150 --> 00:41:25,030
or signs of poisoning.

852
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:27,870
It looks like he was scared to death.

853
00:41:28,180 --> 00:41:29,110
After he died,

854
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:31,430
his liver was taken.

855
00:41:41,670 --> 00:41:43,140
He Chi, the Hot Springs Overseer,

856
00:41:43,140 --> 00:41:45,550
was found dead by River Qu eight days ago.

857
00:41:45,990 --> 00:41:47,710
There's no fatal wound either.

858
00:41:47,710 --> 00:41:49,110
His liver was also taken.

859
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:51,110
Sun Wang, the Chief Musician,

860
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:53,280
died in Pingkang Fang three days ago.

861
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:54,780
According to Deputy President Lu,

862
00:41:54,780 --> 00:41:56,840
the fatal wound was caused by a Mo sword.

863
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:58,450
I agree.

864
00:42:05,290 --> 00:42:06,970
His liver was taken too?

865
00:42:07,310 --> 00:42:07,870
Yes.
